50|$|Other bodies {{predicate}} {{their assessment}} of regularity on the 8th decree of Anderson's Constitution; a Lodge is regular {{if it works}} in conformity {{to the rules of}} its granted constitutional patent. <b>Grand</b> <b>Lodges</b> certify regularity to their recognized Member <b>Lodges</b> and <b>Grand</b> <b>Lodges</b> with patents.|$|R
